    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114100/extras/bebcf2c0be0c16dcf65c68ad072842bf.poster.avif?t=1757028090\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114100/extras/bebcf2c0be0c16dcf65c68ad072842bf.webm?t=1757028090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114100/extras/bebcf2c0be0c16dcf65c68ad072842bf.mp4?t=1757028090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Congratulations! Fresh off the farm and out of the circuit-barn, you've been selected as a member of the Agrifront Circuit Engineers. You've finally got the chance to help out the war effort. Put out your pipe and grab your multimeter - you've got a job to do, Technician. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114100/extras/75cc28a835e8f1fcc5c64a44c9b64cf0.poster.avif?t=1757028090\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114100/extras/75cc28a835e8f1fcc5c64a44c9b64cf0.webm?t=1757028090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114100/extras/75cc28a835e8f1fcc5c64a44c9b64cf0.mp4?t=1757028090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve handcrafted and increasingly complicated levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimize your solutions to increase your score</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the conflict between the Agrifront and the Assembly. Rewire everything from 3D printers to APCs</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete optional sections to unlock collectibles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the rustic soundtrack and pixel art visuals</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114100/extras/c55a7483884795e9faf4406feb3d8948.avif?t=1757028090\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114100/extras_big/c55a7483884795e9faf4406feb3d8948.avif?t=1757028090 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
